{"tid":1784751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(今天沒有極限)  習近平「封神」 與毛像同受民眾燒香膜拜","createTime":"2019-12-16T02:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T08:23:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d172b323d8bb677b0943857835a81989cff6a5d9","tid":1784751,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/12/15/3009955_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F12%2F15%2F3009955_1_1.jpg&h=c3afa924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（影片擷圖）<br />\n<br />\n關注中國宗教自由和人權狀況的線上雜誌《寒冬》（ Bitter Winter ）15日公佈一段7月間拍攝的影片，顯示河南省汝州市一座名為「中原一點紅」的廟內，供桌上擺放著香爐和祭品，一名女士對著習近平和毛澤東畫像先三鞠躬，再三敬軍禮，然後跪地三拜九叩首，對習近平的造神行動又達到一個新境界<br />\n<br />\n這座廟外還有一尊露天毛澤東漢白玉石像，毛像前方桌上擺滿了供品，旁邊立著一座香爐。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，該廟2017年建造至今已投資了十幾萬元人民幣，還要繼續擴建。去年10月，毛澤東像開光時，約有1000多人前來參加。<br />\n<br />\n當地一個村民說：「廟主是跟著形勢走，都得拜毛澤東，別處的廟被扒了，建造毛澤東廟不扒，誰敢扒就犯法，還得判刑。」。<br />\n<br />\n「習近平還活著就給他上香，他知道了是否願意？」另一個村民對供奉習近平畫像表示質疑。<br />\n<br />\n「他肯定願意，到處都是習近平的畫像，連貧困戶家庭都貼著他和毛澤東的像。你不貼習近平的像還不行呢，咱是按著上頭的政策走。」一名來此祭拜的香客說。<br />\n<br />\n中國官媒近年對國家主席習近平個人高度宣傳，力道達毛澤東以降高峰，這讓外界普遍認為，中國正上演一齣造神戲碼。<br />\n<br />\n在大量佛寺道觀被查封、拆毀的同時，供奉中共領導人的廟宇卻香火旺盛。《寒冬》此前報導，有消息顯示，毛澤東、習近平的雕塑與畫像現已陸續進駐各宗教場所，顯示習近平「企圖成為中國人唯一上帝」的野心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/12/15/3009955_2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F12%2F15%2F3009955_2_1.jpg&h=28981227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廟外的露天毛澤東雕像和香爐。（擷取自《寒冬》雜誌）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3009955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3009955&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=df5dcdfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3009955&h=a4f635eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3009955</a>"},{"pid":"f3d8a7ca4fca27886d4a0fa427dd26c09c335b03","tid":1784751,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地要拜咪由尻佢囉<br />\n<br />\n中國有宗教自由嘛"},{"pid":"5fd8435e41e98f39e5c93a6f9839f74e7313e9c8","tid":1784751,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"屎毛教<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fd725be4b6da344559a1faaedfd33e19ac2a84","tid":1784751,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79065c86dc5b98d6d7f130c4d19ca746df8dee9","tid":1784751,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:53:52.000Z","msg":"重要！大家要小心「e肚仔」呢個app！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786046</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"39b700797b146cbe625b92d41a2801ed9f997473","tid":1784751,"uid":23190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:54:44.000Z","msg":"未死就食香好咩"},{"pid":"d8849797b0ad1228996facca4f2906fd359c6080","tid":1784751,"uid":7609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:54:54.000Z","msg":"邪神就有份 全黨死清光"},{"pid":"571018b83a7191f59153c4c022022a6f33b616ff","tid":1784751,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:05:23.000Z","msg":"電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec9f6bc64be7022bd29ee7590d4e0e0abc65c8d","tid":1784751,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm